        <h1>Brewing Methods</h1>
        <hr/>
        <p>
            If you're a coffee or tea lover, you know that the way you brew your drink can significantly
            impact its flavor and aroma. In this article, we'll explore various brewing methods
            and the techniques used to make the perfect cup of coffee or tea.
        </p>

